<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="7663e7c0-da9c-4cbd-94f5-52cb7630eff9" >

    <p>The Research Accounting Team will continue to support the Research Community remotely as Ryerson shifts to essential services only.&nbsp;All information regarding&nbsp;Ryerson Research Accounting&nbsp;can be found on the <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/financial-services/research-accounting/">Financial Services</a>&nbsp;website.</p> 
<p>In light of disruptions related to COVID-19, Canada’s federal research grant and funding agencies have extended deadlines for submitting financial reports. Find more on the <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/financial-services/news/2020/04/tri-agency-financial-reporting-extensions/">tri-agency financial reporting extensions</a>.</p> 
<h4>Policy regarding travel insurance</h4> 
<p>Information regarding&nbsp;travel cancellations&nbsp;can be found on the Financial Services website under&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/financial-services/research-accounting/eligible-research-expenses/">Eligible Research Expenses / Travel Cancellations</a>.</p>
    





