            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1595874171541-professional-expense-reimbursement-funds--perf--and-fund-13-internal-research-funds" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1595874171541-professional-expense-reimbursement-funds--perf--and-fund-13-internal-research-funds" aria-controls="accordion-content-1595874171541-professional-expense-reimbursement-funds--perf--and-fund-13-internal-research-funds" aria-expanded="false">
                            Professional Expense Reimbursement Funds (PERF) and Fund-13 Internal Research Funds
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1595874171541-professional-expense-reimbursement-funds--perf--and-fund-13-internal-research-funds" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1595874171541-professional-expense-reimbursement-funds--perf--and-fund-13-internal-research-funds">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1595874171541 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="f526b8b3-8497-4aca-a2ee-ab5b535d3fa2" >

    <p>Similar to the federal granting agencies advisory of March 6, 2020, regarding COVID-19,&nbsp;Ryerson University will allow eligible reimbursements for cancelled&nbsp;trips in cases such as cancelled conferences, travel advisories, or a personal choice due to health or other concerns.</p> 
<p>Non-refundable travel expenses related to research are eligible for reimbursement when purchased through internal research funds or Professional Expense Reimbursement Funds&nbsp;(PERF). Also, academic/pedagogical currency-related travel expenses claimed through (PERF) are also eligible for reimbursement. Travel/conference cancellation insurance is also an eligible expense if paid for through PERF or internal research funds.</p> 
<p>To be clear, if someone is not traveling to a conference, the non-refundable expenses are eligible for reimbursement.&nbsp;The individual will not receive any additional funds&nbsp;in&nbsp;their PERF or internal research account. Questions regarding PERF expenses can be directed to&nbsp;<a href="mailto:vpfa@ryerson.ca">vpfa@ryerson.ca</a>.&nbsp; Questions regarding internal research fund expenses can be directed to Aimee Kozai (<a href="mailto:akozai@ryerson.ca">akozai@ryerson.ca</a>).</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#f526b8b3-8497-4aca-a2ee-ab5b535d3fa2");});</script></div>

